## 🔧 Technical Details

### Changed Files
1. **web/control/control.js** (main logic)
   - +67 lines: Fuzzy matching utilities (506-573)
   - +32 lines: Modified activeContextOrWarn()
   - +22 lines: Updated buildAppliedAuditEntry()
   - +29 lines: Tag event listeners (3217-3243)
   - +80 lines: Tag rendering functions (966-1044)
   - +31 lines: Updated submitScoringAction()
   - +2 lines: Updated submitProposal()

2. **web/control/index.html** (UI form)
   - Simplified scoring section (lines 63-124)
   - Removed complex nested event selects
   - Added 3-step form structure
   - Added collapsible tag selector

3. **web/control/control.css** (styling)
   - +92 lines: New form & tag styles (1614-1705)
   - Better visual hierarchy
   - Smooth animations

### Not Changed
- Firestore rules (existing rules still work; updated rules ready to deploy)
- House cards & quick buttons (still work the same)
- History display (shows eventTag once filtering is added)
- Place awards system (unchanged)
- Approval queue (unchanged)
- All existing data (fully backward compatible)

---

## ⚡ Performance Notes

- Tag search debounced at 150ms (no lag on typing)
- Fuzzy matching is O(n*m) but catalog is small (~50 items max)
- No new API calls; all local
- CSS animations are GPU-accelerated

