## 📞 Questions?

- **"Why remove the event context gate?"**
  - Most helpers just need to add points fast
  - Events are often repetitive (same 3-4 sports)
  - Tag system is faster + more flexible

- **"Will old data still work?"**
  - Yes! eventTag is optional
  - Old points without tags load fine
  - No breaking changes

- **"Can I still use the complex event structure?"**
  - Yes! Event context still exists if you need it
  - New system is optional, not forced

- **"How do I customize tags?"**
  - Currently uses eventCatalog data
  - Admin UI for tag management coming next

